						<summary>

						<p>Hero-stone (No. II) set up in the Basavēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Sōmēśvara (Undated).</p>						

						<p>This damaged inscription refers to reign of Sōmēśvara and the extant details of date are Chaitra, Sunday. Seems to record death of Bīra-(gāmuṇḍa) of Abbalūr in a fight.</p>						

